summary: An ordinance cancellating the sale of certain property in Section 9, Township 25 North, Range 4 East, W. M. under Ordinance No. 77165; authorizing a refund of $1000.00 paid on the purchase price thereof; making an appropriation from the Emergency Fund; providing for reimbursement from the Park Fund and repealing said Ordinance No. 77165.
committee: Finance and Parks and Public Grounds
